# The generated mirror corpus + scoreboard runs are large
# (~500 MB at default size) and reproducible from the generator,
# so we don't commit them. The generator itself + scoring scripts
# are versioned.
mirror/corpus/
results/*.json
!results/.gitkeep
# Baselines ARE committed — they pin known-good scoreboard
# numbers a regression should turn red. Convention: name
# `baseline-<scale>-<seed>-seed<N>.json`.
!results/baseline-*.json
